      <title>Milei签署执行法令，以支持阿根廷的IMF计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/argentina-s-milei-signs-executive-decree-to-back-imf-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·米利（Javier Milei）周一签署了一项紧急行政法令，要求在阿根廷与国际货币基金组织之间达成一项新协议，这表明员工级协议比以往任何时候都更近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/argentina-s-milei-signs-executive-decree-to-back-imf-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 00:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
